Employment Lawyer 2-3PQE, Dubai
Employment Lawyer 2-3PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
An excellent opportunity has arisen for an Employment lawyer 2-3PQE, to join this top tier international law firm in their Dubai office.
The firm's highly regarded employment law team handles a wide range of top quality contentious and non-contentious work for public and private sector employers including advisory work, disputes related work, document production and transaction/outsourcing work.
In order to be considered for either role, you need to have experience of both contentious and non-contentious employment law. You will be expected to assist on client development and marketing initiatives, so an interest and experience in this will be beneficial.
